text:

However, he does appear to be sporting a hint of a smile in the second picture. 
"Me and my Sainty boo a few months ago...," she wrote alongside it. Kim and Kourtney Kardashian take their kids to have lunch with Kim's husband Kanye West at Something's Fishy in Woodland Hills, California. (Photo: FameFlynet) Kim Kardashian, North West, Saint West and Jonathan Cheban Lunching at Cipriani Restaurant in NYC (Photo: Splash News) 
These latest cute shots come weeks after Kim opened up the Costa Rica family album. 
In pictures uploaded to her website, the reality can be seen playing in the holiday home's luxury pool as she throws her 14-month-old baby boy in the air as he beams and laughs along. 
In another of the snaps, Saint looks intrigued by a camera while doting mum Kim shows him the device and gives him a cuddle.
